en_299333_0	Brigadier V Weerakkody assumes office as new Director of Directorate of Electrical and Mechanical Engineers on Thursday (13) with religious observances.
en_299333_1	He succeeded Major General M.A.A.D Sirinaga.
en_299333_2	Prior to this appointment he has held the appointment of Centre Commandant, Sri Lanka Electrical and Mechanical Engineers Regimental Centre.
en_299333_3	Staff Officers and few Other Ranks of the Directorate were at the venue.
